mobile/README.md:9:- No betting links, purchase prompts, stake sizing, guaranteed-return language, or real-money gambling flow.
mobile/README.md:40:The app sends only anonymous product events: app open, screen view, tab selection, race context changes, analysis request/result/error, latency, market state, and coarse confidence percentages. It does not send participant names, horse/rider names, user IDs, device IDs, betting selections, or meet names. Keep the endpoint server-side so beta retention, session length, analysis-start rate, detail-view rate, and Pro-screen drop-off can be measured without adding third-party tracking.
